            "text": "BFCL (Gorilla project, UC Berkeley) provides the most detailed breakdown of function-calling accuracy. Its 2,000+ test cases span seven categories, each isolating a distinct failure mode. The live leaderboard is updated as providers release new models."
          }
        ]
