      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Common Pitfalls"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Argument type mismatch — the model passes a string where an integer is required. Fix: include explicit types in tool descriptions and use Pydantic to validate before calling."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Hallucinated parameters — the model invents an argument name not in the schema. Fix: enforce strict JSON schema validation; reject any call with extra fields."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Wrong tool order — the model calls tool B before tool A when B depends on A's output. Fix: add a planning step that outputs an ordered call list before executing."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Parallel calls serialized — the model emits calls one at a time when they could run concurrently. Fix: explicitly prompt the model that independent calls should be returned in a single response as a list."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Over-calling — the model calls a tool it already called with the same arguments. Fix: maintain a call log in the context window and instruct the model to check it before repeating a call."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
